room_title: Escape room "Prison Escape" by San Antonio Panic Room in San Antonio
review: Our family had so much fun doing the Prison Break yesterday. Challenging, fun, and a little bit of panicking. Ricardo was an awesome team member, and we can't wait to do it again! Get over here and do this!

room_title: Escape room "Prison Escape" by San Antonio Panic Room in San Antonio
review: Excellent! This was great for me and my family. Having two teens and 10-year-old, this activity engaged all of us and encouraged us to work together even though we were in a different cell block (we did the Prison rooms). Great time had by all!
